{"tid":385202,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 樓下住咗隻顛雞........","createTime":"2017-09-03T04:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T23:58:09.000Z","uid":139252,"like":1270,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24cd417f4594c98983efce846003b6f42d9fa7f7","tid":385202,"uid":139252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T04:45:15.000Z","msg":"話說我樓下有個獨居嘅廢中 佢隔一排就會走上嚟撳門鐘 平均一個月一次 高鋒時期就兩星期一次 話我行路成日砰砰聲好撚嘈<br />\n開頭我都認有時冇著拖鞋行係會咁 加上依家啲樓啲牆薄到仆街 應聲都唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但之後我已經keep 著拖鞋行 拉櫈又特登拎起再放底 佢都仲走上嚟撳鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有次夜晚條顛雞又走上嚟問我聽唔聽到行雷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我心諗屌你老母聽到又點聽唔到又點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果搞到依家我屋企所有野同地面接觸嘅時候都要小心翼翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為左隻顛雞唔好再上嚟我已經好辛苦 我應該點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  砰大聲啲 煩撚到佢仆街為止<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  算啦 就吓啲廢中"},{"pid":"a0dcc6b0ea423feeb31695014553825e472e7324","tid":385202,"uid":33717,"like":633,"dislike":1,"score":632,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T04:46:46.000Z","msg":"你又走上樓上撳鐘同佢講<br />\n睇佢點反應 之後抄佢個解決方法"},{"pid":"473a7c75f048ddb16aa68d3901e120bd952f8c08","tid":385202,"uid":122331,"like":354,"dislike":1,"score":353,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T04:48:39.000Z","msg":"再拉櫈 大撚大力咁拉<br />\n落去尻㩒鐘 撚返佢轉頭 有無聽到行雷<br />\n佢答完你<br />\n<br />\n你再返上去 再拉櫈<br />\n撚到佢收皮"},{"pid":"df1b4b7a5b1b5c6db430d692a3a4c24f59b22e4b","tid":385202,"uid":22743,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T04:49:03.000Z","msg":"同管理員講下?"},{"pid":"e74b6493e3de621cf5239d489305104036c3c789","tid":385202,"uid":22743,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T